  "prompt": "Where is the best guitar buying shop in Guwahati?",
  "response": "While the concept of the \"best\" guitar shop can be subjective depending on individual preferences and needs, some popular and well-regarded places to buy guitars in Guwahati include:\n\n1. **Musical Village**: Known for its range of musical instruments, Musical Village offers a good selection of guitars and other related accessories.\n\n2. **Furtados**: Furtados is a recognized music store chain across India that offers a wide variety of guitars and other musical instruments, accessories, and sheet music.\n\n3. **OnStage Guitar Shop**: This store specializes in guitars and related gear, and is well-regarded by local musicians.\n\n4. **S.M. Music World**: Another popular shop that offers a variety of musical instruments, including guitars.\n\nIt's always a good idea to check online reviews, visit the shops personally, and consult with local musicians to find the store that best meets your specific needs.",
